      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just wanting to \"explore other options\" though. it feels more like there's nothing left to explore. i've poured everything into this and there's nothing left of me. it's like i'm just a ghost inhabiting a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. i just want the noise to stop. everything is just... so heavy.",
